                                    <p>You do not have to do everything at once, try one thing at a time and find what works for you.</p>
                                    <ul class="nhsuk-list nhsuk-list--tick">

                                        <li>
                                            
                                                
                                            
                                            <p data-block-key="x57ek">get active for 150 minutes a week – you can break this up into shorter sessions</p>
                                        </li>

                                        <li>
                                            
                                                
                                            
                                            <p data-block-key="otqlp">aim to get your 5 A Day – 80g of fresh, canned or frozen fruit or vegetables count as 1 portion</p>
                                        </li>

                                        <li>
                                            
                                                
                                            
                                            <p data-block-key="otqlp">aim to lose 1 to 2lbs, or 0.5 to 1kg, a week</p>
