                                        <li>
                                            
                                                
                                            
                                            <p data-block-key="otqlp">read food labels – products with more green colour coding than amber and red are often a healthier option</p>
                                        </li>

                                        <li>
                                            
                                                
                                            
                                            <p data-block-key="otqlp">swap sugary drinks for water – if you do not like the taste, add slices of lemon or lime for flavour</p>
                                        </li>

                                        <li>
                                            
                                                
                                            
                                            <p data-block-key="otqlp">cut down on food that&#x27;s high in sugar and fat – start by swapping sugary cereal for wholegrain alternatives</p>
